1|[HELP]|1|This is a help message!
2|CCSTEP1|1|Recipe Name
3|RECIPEIN|1|To prepare this recipe, you need to place a %1s in the kitchen.
4|RECIPEIN|2|The green color means you already own this facility. If the color is red, make sure you place one in your kitchen!
5|RECIPEIN|3|Award-winning dish
